### Styles API

| Styles API   | Type                             | Default     | Annotation                                    |
| ------------ | -------------------------------- | ----------- | --------------------------------------------- |
| unstyled`?`  | `boolean`                        | `false`     | if `true`, all default styles will be removed |
| underline`?` | `"always" \| "hover" \| "never"` | `never`     |                                               |
| role`?`      | `"anchor" \| AriaRole`           | `undefined` | if `role="anchor"`, add blue color style      |

